com.radiotelescope.repository.role

Class UserRole

  • com.radiotelescope.repository.role.UserRole

  • public class UserRole

    Entity class used to store a class User Entity's roles. These roles are used with Spring Security to validate the actions a class User is able to execute.

    This Entity correlates to the UserRole SQL Table.
